the tearing down of Saddam Hussein's Statue, 
is depicted. 

43
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:10,100
The frame is however quite different,

44
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:13,800
thereby probably changing how we deconstruct 
the message.

45
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:18,800
We can see that these types of theories no 
longer focus on the intention of the sender 

46
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:22,566
but rather on message construction and 
deconstruction.

47
00:03:22,566 --> 00:03:25,232
So no longer the linear effect oriented approach

48
00:03:25,233 --> 00:03:28,599
but a focus on the construction and the 
reception of a message.

49
